西班牙裔人的祖先分布广泛，族群多样性非常强。因此西班牙裔并不是一个[[种族|种族]]，而更像一类[[族群|族群]]，以語言和文化维繫。

==西班牙裔和拉丁裔和西班牙人的区别==
'''西班牙裔'''（Hispanic）和'''拉丁裔'''（Latino）经常会被人们混用。事实上，西班牙裔的定义相比而言较为广义，指的是说[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]的人或者祖籍为[[西班牙|西班牙]]的人；而拉丁裔的则较为狭义，指的是拥有狭义[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]祖先的人们（因此还包括[[巴西人|巴西人]]，尽管大部分巴西人说[[葡萄牙语|葡萄牙语]]），这里的狭义指代的是以[[拉丁语族|拉丁语族]]语言为官方语言的美洲国家和地区，即西班牙语、葡萄牙语以及法语，注意英语和荷兰语不属于拉丁语族。<ref name="Dejud2007">{{cite book|author=Carlos Dejud|title=The Relationship Among Ethnic Identity, Psychological Well-being, Academic Achievement, and Intergroup Competence of School-age Hispanic/Latino Youth|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=G6h6I0trgKUC&pg=PA21|year=2007|publisher=ProQuest|isbn=978-0-549-29853-3|page=21|access-date=2014-03-14|archive-date=2016-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426064138/https://books.google.com/books?id=G6h6I0trgKUC&pg=PA21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Ready1991">{{cite book|author=Timothy Ready|title=Latino Immigrant Youth: Passages from Adolescence to Adulthood|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Qz3gHaea22MC&pg=PA14|year=1991|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-0-8153-0057-1|page=14|access-date=2014-03-14|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420222855/https://books.google.com/books?id=Qz3gHaea22MC&pg=PA14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://csuchico-dspace.calstate.edu/handle/10211.4/222 |title=Latino: People with roots in the Spanish- and Portuguese-speaking Americas. This broader term, mostly used in the United States, is sometimes used as a replacement for Hispanic. |accessdate=2014-03-14 |archive-date=2014-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018161553/http://csuchico-dspace.calstate.edu/handle/10211.4/222 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://americanhistory.si.edu/collections/mexicanamerica/glossary.html |title=Defining "Hispanic" as meaning those with Spanish speaking roots in the Americas and "Latino" as meaning those with both Spanish- and Portuguese-speaking roots in Latin America. |access-date=2014-03-14 |archive-date=2008-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/200806210